### readme version v9.5
   all scripts adapted to updating blacklisted domains in BIND9 - Response Policy Zone
   version v9.5 of all scripts are the next release after the earlier release.
   it's a maintenance release that increases version compatibility with list of urls in grab_urls

### author:
   ngadimin@warnet-ersa.net
   https://github.com/ngadmini/

